{"tid":596593,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺連登仔好易比報紙佬煽動","createTime":"2018-03-17T19:09:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-19T01:12:08.000Z","uid":27008,"like":91,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"269c9f072119ef7e365f8b6d7b41e8cf7e4295be","tid":596593,"uid":27008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T19:09:35.000Z","msg":"果位因手術失敗而中風既女仔的確好慘<br />\n但報紙佬幾句就將手術風險變成對醫生負面既字眼<br />\n<br />\n有人為醫生平反，指出插錯係手術風險，醫生對手唔係機器，點都會有機會犯錯，所以先放落手術風險，作為個女監護人既媽咪假設有認真睇張consent form就應該好清楚<br />\n<br />\n依班人客觀為醫生平反，換黎既係：鬼唔望你將來都係咁<br />\n<br />\n玩下文字藝術，引起公眾迴響先係佢地目的，因為咁先多人睇多人關注<br />\n或者咁講，如果佢地寫：年輕女孩因進行高風險手術以致中風，恐毀一生<br />\n咁報會有咁多聲音咩<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17943b61eaf552d64e18f9cab723577b678b7b8c","tid":596593,"uid":49215,"like":29,"dislike":4,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T19:26:17.000Z","msg":"依加D人好似覺得醫生要100%醫得返人咁"},{"pid":"c3bcd8f6af447e8e1baca470d759e5ede52247a0","tid":596593,"uid":152437,"like":36,"dislike":3,"score":33,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T19:32:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"599c33c511828e383e4621fa3e1d56e0b0ffe34b","tid":596593,"uid":136186,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T19:33:47.000Z","msg":"上緊連登啲人個腦好似停咗咁"},{"pid":"ad9632848c0911301a64aac5e83810c0c9e17181","tid":596593,"uid":89134,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"c3bcd8f6af447e8e1baca470d759e5ede52247a0","tid":596593,"uid":152437,"like":36,"dislike":3,"score":33,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T19:32:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T19:34:09.000Z","msg":"笑甚麼 畜牲 你也是連登仔"},{"pid":"f79b1bc8cc38839cfc4b6ab27f6af0ecfefde771","tid":596593,"uid":117,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T19:35:08.000Z","msg":"九成連登仔都冇獨立思考能力<br />\n求其搵d五毛假膠都耍到佢地氹氹轉<br />\n更何況傳媒界<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf